article.description: — Cameron Christon's 15 points helped Grambling defeat Dartmouth 73-49 on Monday night.
article.headline: Christon scores 15, Grambling downs Dartmouth 73-49
article.story: SAN ANTONIO -- — Cameron Christon's 15 points helped Grambling defeat Dartmouth 73-49 on Monday night. Christon added seven rebounds for the Tigers (4-3). Virshon Cotton scored 15 points and added five rebounds and three steals. Carte'Are Gordon shot 5 of 12 from the field to finish with 12 points, while adding 11 rebounds. Ryan Cornish led the way for the Big Green (2-5) with 13 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
